.oh-my-zsh/

# Machine-specific kanshi profiles — monitor make/model/serial must not land in this
# public repo. Stowed alongside the tracked skeleton, which `include`s them.
# The directory itself stays tracked (via .gitkeep) so the include glob always resolves.
config-stow/kanshi/kanshi/config.d/*
!config-stow/kanshi/kanshi/config.d/.gitkeep
